data.description: Check out this stunningly upgraded estate home in the Champions Gate Golf Country Club community! The Grande Charleston model exudes a welcoming vibe, boasting a front porch and new French doors. Stepping inside, you're greeted by a spacious foyer, living, and dining area adorned with premium paint and Porcelain tile. The kitchen, to the right, features 42-inch tray wood cabinetry, stainless steel hardware, an oversized quartz island complemented by matching countertops, elegant pendant lighting, LED fixtures, subway backsplash tile, and GE appliances.  The cozy family room with sliding doors to the pool deck is perfect for unwinding. On the left wing, discover the executive master bedroom suite with a tray ceiling, sliding doors, two walk in closets, a beautifully tiled bathroom suite with a garden tub, separate shower, and an office/den drenched in natural light with a beautiful built-in library area. The second and third bedrooms share a full hallway bath, while the fourth bedroom connects to another full bath with pool access. The second level features a full bath and a generous loft area, ideal for the perfect home entertainment experience.  The laundry room comes equipped with a GE Profile Series washer/dryer, and leads to the 3 car garage with newly laid Epoxy flooring and plenty of room for your cars and golf cart, aswell as additional garage storage and attic addition. Step onto your covered pool deck overlooking the oversized lot, with an oversized spa big enough for ten people, and a large pool stylishly designed by the current owners, complete with LED lighting. There is also an outdoor kitchen area with so much private space to sit and enjoy the stunning outdoor surroundings this gorgeous home has to offer. Upgraded landscaping, irrigation, ceiling fans, stucco elevation, clay tile roof, rain gutters, lighting and much more add to this home's allure.  The amenities at the Oasis Clubhouse and Water Park are truly spectacular, featuring a lazy river, water slides, pools for all ages, a spa, restaurants, bars, a theater, games room, fitness center, and cabanas. But wait, there's more! The Country Club boasts a private clubhouse exclusively for primary residents, offering dining, business facilities, pools, a spa, and lounging areas.  This energy-efficient, solar powered secure home comes with HOA fees that cover cable, internet, landline telephone, home security, gated community access, lawn care, landscaping, golf membership, clubhouse access, business center usage, and even a monthly restaurant credit. It's a true value for what it offers! Come and see for yourself.
